name: So What if I Transmigrated into a Honkai Beast?
summary: From mosquito to Star God.From the Previous Era to Honkai: Star Rail.This is a path of non-human evolution, a path of empire establishment, spanning the Honkai Universe.The first half is pure - Honkai Previous Era (the pure Honkai storyline ends here);The interlude will be a Genshin Impact short story (the author's nonsensical prophecies);The second half will be Honkai: Star Rail (a story of the interstellar cosmos, various Neta, and a few elements from the Honkai Current Era).
